option.helptext:
Sets the chance when visiting a zone that an eligible bones file will be searched for and, if found, loaded into a zone.

{{c|}} almost never - {{C|0.1%}}
{{c|}} rarely - {{C|0.5%}}
{{c|}} uncommon - {{C|1.25%}}
{{c|}} default - {{C|2.0%}}
{{c|}} sometimes - {{C|5.0%}}
{{c|}} frequently - {{C|10.0%}}
{{c|}} often - {{C|20.0%}}
{{c|}} not quite half - {{C|40.0%}}
{{c|}} custom - enables a button to enter a {{C|custom value}}

Keep in mind, humans are notoriously bad at judging probability.

Note: if you would like to disable encountering bones altogether, there is a debug option (in the {{c|Debug}} category) to pause bones encounters.

The default is {{W|2.0%}}.
